{"tid":572031,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"弓起巴士司機成為香港第一賤既職業","createTime":"2018-02-25T08:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-26T13:41:22.000Z","uid":9683,"like":20,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3830c653edbcf0cee3277a49191bbad26d5553cb","tid":572031,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:33:41.000Z","msg":"唔只需要車牌，仲需要有揸大車既技術，每日揸10幾個鐘，唔好同我講容易，你自己揸下就知係幾費神，話揸巴士容易個D肯定冇車牌。<br />\n<br />\nEQ需要極高，下下比市民屌，公司又唔照你，上又屌，下又屌。冇咁上下EQ都唔好做。<br />\n<br />\n人工低，對比起做食Q，每日坐係度玩下電話又一日都拎到皮3~4，做巴士司機咁辛苦2皮野都冇，仲賤撚過食Q，人工又差唔多，點解我唔做食Q?<br />\n<br />\n公司西，香港既公司西就係人都知，依家公司夾9你班巴士佬，你地連基本既抗爭都唔肯做，奴性!<br />\n<br />\n總結:，份工又要有一定既要求，又要日日比人屌，又冇得升一世做巴士司機，我做份食Q都有前途過佢啦，同事又唔會幫手出聲，我點解要做巴士司機唔搵過份，咁都唔係香港第一賤工?"},{"pid":"a40c817c9392a0b2e4597120f7ff80998faba17a","tid":572031,"uid":9683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes50.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"545d738f4a097a4af0fb3f7bf5b242f5488805b2","tid":572031,"uid":129004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"自己來黎"},{"pid":"55990d15e506afb05cc68c5d722ca60a169eccbe","tid":572031,"uid":129004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"545d738f4a097a4af0fb3f7bf5b242f5488805b2","tid":572031,"uid":129004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:43:23.000Z","msg":"自己來黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:43:38.000Z","msg":"自己攞黎"},{"pid":"84e73847a8d706ab2dec068b1b881d132c89a899","tid":572031,"uid":82532,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:54:23.000Z","msg":"「第一賤業」咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdede562dcb607a71eb5ccf1948da62f286d296","tid":572031,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T08:56:00.000Z","msg":"唔準話巴士佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931762953c16c6345dc703e22e07d4cd3c6887